* Note: Iris is a computer program with artificial intelligence she cannot 
move at all except through the Ark's systems. Besides, she has a steady 
power supply, I admit that it will run out eventually but one single charge 
won't take the shield down. She's a defence system and is doing all she is 
capable of to defend the Ark from Predacon attack. Remember, she is also a 
back up system and when(or if) the Ark's own systems start running properly 
she'll stop and let it take over again, until then it is her job to protect 
the ship. Thank you.)

* Zyber looked at Rowdy Wolf and sighed, why was he so edgy around her? 
Besides the fact that she was new to him he should at least begin to relax a 
little. She looked out at the field around them, the small herd of deer had 
moved on and was now a good hundred meters away.
Her stomach growled as a swift wind picked up and ruffled her fur.
It was beginning to get a little cold but she was used to it, her arctic 
home made sure of that.*
